[{"categories":[],"content":"Fuck","date":"2023-10-12","objectID":"https://lv123123long.github.io/%E5%89%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/","series":[],"tags":[],"title":"前置参数介绍","uri":"https://lv123123long.github.io/%E5%89%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/"},{"categories":[],"content":" Monday","date":"2023-10-12","objectID":"https://lv123123long.github.io/%E5%89%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/:0:0","series":[],"tags":[],"title":"前置参数介绍","uri":"https://lv123123long.github.io/%E5%89%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/#monday"},{"categories":[],"content":" helaosh jiandage libo ","date":"2023-10-12","objectID":"https://lv123123long.github.io/%E5%89%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/:1:0","series":[],"tags":[],"title":"前置参数介绍","uri":"https://lv123123long.github.io/%E5%89%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/#helaosh"},{"categories":null,"content":" My blog","date":"2023-10-10","objectID":"https://lv123123long.github.io/my_blog/:0:0","series":null,"tags":null,"title":"My_blog","uri":"https://lv123123long.github.io/my_blog/#my-blog"},{"categories":null,"content":" hugo.toml hugo serve 的默认运行环境是 development, 而 hugo 的默认运行环境是 production. 由于本地 development 环境的限制, 评论系统, CDN 和 fingerprint 不会在 development 环境下启用. 你可以使用 hugo serve -e production 命令来开启这些特性. ","date":"2023-10-10","objectID":"https://lv123123long.github.io/my_blog/:1:0","series":null,"tags":null,"title":"My_blog","uri":"https://lv123123long.github.io/my_blog/#hugotoml"},{"categories":null,"content":" CDN配置CDN（Content Delivery Network）是一种通过在全球各地部署服务器节点来分发网站内容的网络服务。CDN的主要目的是提高网站的访问速度、减轻源服务器负载以及增加网站的可靠性。 CDN配置的作用是将网站的静态资源（如图片、CSS、JavaScript等）缓存到CDN服务器上，并通过CDN网络将这些资源分发给用户。具体的CDN配置包括以下几个方面： 域名解析：将需要加速的域名（如static.example.com）通过DNS解析指向CDN服务商提供的域名服务器。 加速区域选择：根据网站受众的地理位置，选择合适的CDN服务器节点部署区域，以便更快地将内容传输给用户。 缓存策略配置：根据网站的需求，设置CDN节点对静态资源的缓存时间、缓存容量、缓存更新机制等，以提供更好的用户体验和缓解源服务器压力。 URL重写：将网站的资源URL重写为CDN服务器的地址，使用户请求的资源能够经由CDN节点获取，而不是直接请求源服务器。 HTTPS支持：配置CDN证书，使CDN节点能够支持网站的HTTPS加密传输，确保数据的安全性。 ","date":"2023-10-10","objectID":"https://lv123123long.github.io/my_blog/:2:0","series":null,"tags":null,"title":"My_blog","uri":"https://lv123123long.github.io/my_blog/#cdn配置"},{"categories":null,"content":" 博客创建过程记录","date":"2023-10-10","objectID":"https://lv123123long.github.io/libo/:0:0","series":null,"tags":null,"title":"Libo","uri":"https://lv123123long.github.io/libo/#博客创建过程记录"},{"categories":null,"content":" 下载hugo 官网下载，，扩展版本的hugo 添加到环境变量，查看hugo是否可用 ","date":"2023-10-10","objectID":"https://lv123123long.github.io/libo/:1:0","series":null,"tags":null,"title":"Libo","uri":"https://lv123123long.github.io/libo/#下载hugo"},{"categories":null,"content":" 查找主题 hugo官网主题查找 我选择的是dolt主题 https://github.com/HEIGE-PCloud/DoIt/blob/main/README.zh-cn.md https://hugodoit.pages.dev/zh-cn/theme-documentation-basics/ ","date":"2023-10-10","objectID":"https://lv123123long.github.io/libo/:2:0","series":null,"tags":null,"title":"Libo","uri":"https://lv123123long.github.io/libo/#查找主题"},{"categories":null,"content":" 主题使用记录 git submodule add https://github.com/HEIGE-PCloud/DoIt.git themes/DoIt 将这个主题仓库添加为你的网站目录的子模块。 git submodule update --remote --merge 通过这条命令来将主题更新至最新版本。 修改hugo的配置文件","date":"2023-10-10","objectID":"https://lv123123long.github.io/libo/:2:1","series":null,"tags":null,"title":"Libo","uri":"https://lv123123long.github.io/libo/#主题使用记录"},{"categories":null,"content":" 主题使用记录 git submodule add https://github.com/HEIGE-PCloud/DoIt.git themes/DoIt 将这个主题仓库添加为你的网站目录的子模块。 git submodule update --remote --merge 通过这条命令来将主题更新至最新版本。 修改hugo的配置文件","date":"2023-10-10","objectID":"https://lv123123long.github.io/libo/:2:1","series":null,"tags":null,"title":"Libo","uri":"https://lv123123long.github.io/libo/#修改hugo的配置文件"},{"categories":null,"content":" 创建新文章 hugo new posts/first_post.md 实时预览 hugo serve --disableFastRender ","date":"2023-10-10","objectID":"https://lv123123long.github.io/libo/:3:0","series":null,"tags":null,"title":"Libo","uri":"https://lv123